# PickHome

Self-hosted apartment scoring for house hunting (German UI). Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind, Prisma + SQLite. No payment integration.

## Repository layout

- `src/app/` — pages, API routes, server actions (`actions.ts`, `totp-actions.ts`)
- `src/lib/` — domain logic (kebab-case filenames)
- `src/components/` — React components (PascalCase)
- `prisma/schema.prisma` — database schema
- `scripts/` — CLI helpers (backup, data dirs)
- `tests/` — Vitest (`unit/`, `integration/`, `helpers/`)
- `data/` — runtime data (gitignored): `pickhome.db`, `uploads/`, `backups/`

Path alias: `@/*` → `src/*`.

## Language

- **UI copy and page metadata:** German (`lang="de"`).
- **Code:** English only — identifiers, comments, commit messages, error keys, tests.

## Auth and roles

- `src/lib/auth.ts`: `getSessionUser()`, `requireUser()`, `requireAdmin()`, `isAdmin()`, `ROLE_ADMIN` / `ROLE_USER`.
- Cookie: `ph_session`.
- Regular users: projects via `ProjectMember`. Admins use `/admin`; redirect admins away from user dashboards (`if (isAdmin(user)) redirect("/admin")`).
- Login and TOTP: `src/app/totp-actions.ts`, `/login`, `/login/totp`, `/account/settings`.

## Data and security

- `PICKHOME_DATA_DIR` (default `./data`), `DATABASE_URL` (SQLite `file:` paths relative to `prisma/`).
- Uploads: `src/lib/pickhome-data.ts`, `src/lib/apartment-media.ts`, served at `/uploads/...`.
- Never commit: `data/`, `.env*`, secrets, `node_modules/`, `.next/`, user databases or backup ZIPs.

## Releases and versioning

- Version source: `"version"` in `package.json`.
- Push to `main` → CI bumps patch (`1.2.0` → `1.2.1`), tags `v*`, and creates a [GitHub Release](https://github.com/n3roGit/PickHome/releases). Set major/minor in `package.json` manually when needed. Docker publish runs on tag push (`n3ro88/pickhome:latest`, `n3ro88/pickhome:1.2.3`, …).
- Update `CHANGELOG.md` manually when releasing.

## Git workflow

- Commit and push when the user asks or after completing a feature batch.
- Do not force-push `main` unless explicitly requested.
- Do not amend commits that were already pushed.

## Commands

- Dev: `npm run dev` (runs `predev` → ensures data dirs)
- DB: `npm run db:push`, `npm run db:seed`
- Tests: `npm test`
- Backup: `npm run data:export` / `data:import`
- Docker image: `n3ro88/pickhome` (see `docker-compose.yml`)

## Feature map (routes)

| Area | Route / tab |
|------|-------------|
| Dashboard | `/dashboard` |
| Project | `/project/[id]` — tabs: apartments, archived, team, settings, criteria, compare, map, calendar |
| Apartment | `/project/[id]/apartment/[aptId]` |
| Admin | `/admin` — users, backup export/import |
| Settings | `/account/settings` — password, TOTP |

Project access: always verify membership (`members: { some: { userId } }` or helpers in `src/lib/project-data.ts`).
